{"data":{"page":{"html":"<h1 id=\"status\"><a href=\"#status\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Status</h1>\n<div class=\"toc\">\n<h2><a href=\"#toc\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Table of Contents</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#introduction\">Introduction</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#sync-versus-async-handlers\">Sync versus Async handlers</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#using-it-with-next\">Using it with next</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"introduction\"><a href=\"#introduction\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Introduction</h2>\n<p>The status is an information indicating whether an action had any impact or not. It's meaning may differ from one action to another. Here are a few examples:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>touching a file<br>\nThe status is \"true\" if the file was created or any metadata associated with the file has changed, such as the modification time or a change of ownership.</li>\n<li>modification of a configuration file (json, yaml, ini...)<br>\nThe status is true if a property or any metadata associated with the file has changed. A change of format, like prettifying the source code, will not affect the status while the addition of a new property and the modification on the value of an existing property will set the status to \"true\".</li>\n<li>checking if a port is open\nThe status is set to \"true\" if a server is listening on that port and \"false\" otherwise. This is arguably an alternative usage. In such case, it is often used conjointly with the \"shy\" option to ensure that parent actions don't get their status modified.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Status is a central concept in Nikita implemented inside every action. Early on, it was decided that actions will be idempotent and indicate whether a change occurred or not. The latter is what we call the status. It is formalized as a simple boolean passed to the callback.</p>\n<p>When a handler is made of multiple child actions, the status will be <code class=\"language-text\">true</code> if at least one of the child action has a status of <code class=\"language-text\">true</code>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"sync-versus-async-handlers\"><a href=\"#sync-versus-async-handlers\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Sync versus Async handlers</h2>\n<p>Asynchronous handlers receive a callback. Once completed, the callback may be called with an error argument followed by an object containing the status property as its second argument or a Boolean value for its shorter version.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'nikita'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Parent action</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">call</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>options<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> callback<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// Do something</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">setImmediate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// Set the status to \"true\", default is \"false\"</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">callback</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">null</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>err<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> status<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// Status is now \"true\"</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">assert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>status<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Synchronuous handlers don't modify the status directly. Instead, the status is derived from its child handlers.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'nikita'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Parent action</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">call</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// Do something</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>err<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>status<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// By default, status is \"false\"</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Parent action</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">call</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// Child action</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">call</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>options<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> callback<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// Set the status to \"true\"</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">callback</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">null</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>err<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>status<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// Status is now \"true\"</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">assert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>status<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"using-it-with-next\"><a href=\"#using-it-with-next\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Using it with <code class=\"language-text\">next</code></h2>\n<p>The <code class=\"language-text\">next</code> function is called once a list of actions has terminated or if any error occurred before. When called, it expect a function with the error and status provided as arguments. Once <code class=\"language-text\">next</code> is called, the status is reset and a new run of actions may be scheduled.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'nikita'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// All actions are false</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">call</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>options<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> callback<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">callback</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">null</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">call</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>options<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> callback<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">callback</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">null</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Then status is false</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">next</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>err<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>status<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">assert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>status<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// One actions is true</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">call</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>options<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> callback<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">callback</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">null</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">call</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>options<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> callback<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">callback</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">null</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">call</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>options<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> callback<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">callback</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">null</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Then status is true</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">next</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>err<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>status<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">assert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>status<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>","fields":{"slug":"/usages/status/","edit_url":"https://github.com/adaltas/node-nikita-docs/edit/master/src/md/usages/status.md"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Status","description":null,"keywords":null}}},"pageContext":{}}